Like a kilo of halva, it's sustenance.

862
00:42:06,000 --> 00:42:09,000
Ne? Ha. Bigir. Ha.
 
Right? Here. Take it. Here.

863
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:11,000
Wara.
 
Come.

864
00:42:11,000 --> 00:42:14,000
Bigir.
 
Take it.

865
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:15,000
