948
00:45:47,000 --> 00:45:51,000
No milet ba'elimê bazar heye, ê potix, ê xidre jî wînin, ê
her tişt kî wînin.
 
No, when the people get used to there being a market, they
will bring melons, they will bring vegetables too, they will
