957
00:46:10,000 --> 00:46:12,000
E hewstiyê me re, hişyê mezin.
 
That is our courtyard, the big courtyard.

958
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:13,000
No ez dibêm hewşê ne mezin e.
 
No, I'm saying the courtyards are big.

959
